{"tid":1056144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吐露港公路撞斃過路女子，司機涉嫌危險駕駛被捕","createTime":"2019-03-11T03:47:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T08:27:10.000Z","uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad835c663ea4c0db133bef3d1854a28a717de45","tid":1056144,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T03:47:57.000Z","msg":"大埔吐露港公路貨車撞斃過路女子<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】大埔吐露港公路凌晨發生致命車禍，一名女子被貨車撞倒，當場死亡。<span style=\"color: red;\">貨車司機涉嫌危險駕駛導致他人死亡被捕。</span><br />\n<br />\n警員用帳篷覆蓋死者遺體，五十六歲貨車司機在警車上協助調查。<br />\n<br />\n凌晨近四時，一輛貨車沿吐露港公路往上水方向行駛至廣福邨對開時，撞倒一名橫過馬路的三十三歲女子。她被捲入車底，身體多處受傷，消防員接報到場將她救出，當場證實死亡，警方正調查意外的原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=340387&amp;fbclid=IwAR1QHVR5OWb-n1PWXcyo-sdpz7mCj487z3oIb9nGWpVmB6J7y8sluIFi4Vo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D340387%26fbclid%3DIwAR1QHVR5OWb-n1PWXcyo-sdpz7mCj487z3oIb9nGWpVmB6J7y8sluIFi4Vo&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FPG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=ef4c0afd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D340387%26fbclid%3DIwAR1QHVR5OWb-n1PWXcyo-sdpz7mCj487z3oIb9nGWpVmB6J7y8sluIFi4Vo&h=40c74050\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=340387&amp;fbclid=IwAR1QHVR5OWb-n1PWXcyo-sdpz7mCj487z3oIb9nGWpVmB6J7y8sluIFi4Vo</a>"},{"pid":"05fb6e43d0c784b3eb5718849c8a8d07df90dc7f","tid":1056144,"uid":40470,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T03:49:59.000Z","msg":"?<br />\n<br />\n吐露港過馬路？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8bf7aa382814004a1195e12caf0ccc9ce4990dc","tid":1056144,"uid":34409,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"05fb6e43d0c784b3eb5718849c8a8d07df90dc7f","tid":1056144,"uid":40470,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T03:49:59.000Z","msg":"?<br />\n<br />\n吐露港過馬路？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal